  "subject": "feat: architecture redesign - Phase 1 foundation",
  "body": "Migrate from vanilla JS to TypeScript + SvelteKit monorepo architecture\nfor improved maintainability, type safety, and testability.\n\nChanges:\n- Add monorepo structure with pnpm workspaces\n- Create @model-pear/calculator package with TypeScript\n  - Extract Model 1 (Cost-Plus) with full type definitions\n  - Add comprehensive test suite (44 tests)\n  - Define types for entities, results, and calculations\n- Create @model-pear/web SvelteKit app shell\n  - Set up Tailwind CSS configuration\n  - Add landing page with mode selector\n  - Add proof-of-concept UI for Model 1\n  - Configure static adapter for GitHub Pages\n- Move existing vanilla JS code to legacy/ folder\n- Add ARCHITECTURE.md documenting the redesign\n\nBuild commands:\n- pnpm install: Install dependencies\n- pnpm test: Run calculator tests\n- pnpm build: Build all packages\n\nThis is Phase 1 of 4 in the migration plan.\nNext: Extract Models 2-6 and projection calculations.",
